dc_title_s: Addresses and Driveways Washburn County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents addresses and driveways for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2019. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Washburn_Addresses_Driveways_2019.gdb'. The features included in this geodatabase are 'Washburn_Addresses_2019' and 'Washburn_Driveways_2019'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://co.washburn.wi.us/gis-data-downloads/
